0.title: Duration by Request
0.query:
timeseries avg(dt.synthetic.http.request.duration), by: { dt.entity.http_check_step }
| fieldsAdd synthetic.http.request.duration = ArrayAvg(`avg(dt.synthetic.http.request.duration)`)
| fieldsAdd name=entityAttr(dt.entity.http_check_step, "entity.name")
| sort synthetic.http.request.duration desc
| limit 20
